d stk--no-padding\"><div class=\"stk--column-flex stk-block-content stk-inner-blocks stk-e0ecbd4-inner-blocks\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-text stk-block-text stk-block stk-809e6fb\" data-block-id=\"809e6fb\">.stk-809e6fb .stk-block-text__text{font-size:50px !important;color:var(--paletteColor5,#ffffff) !important;font-weight:900 !important}@media screen and (max-width:1023px){.stk-809e6fb .stk-block-text__text{font-size:50px !important}}<p class=\"stk-block-text__text has-text-color has-text-align-center\">2013</p></div>\n</div></div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-column stk-block-column stk-column stk-block stk-1fb48d8\" data-v=\"4\" data-block-id=\"1fb48d8\">.stk-1fb48d8{align-self:center !important}@media screen and (min-width:768px){.stk-1fb48d8{flex:1 1 66.7% !important}}<div class=\"stk-column-wrapper stk-block-column__content stk-container stk-1fb48d8-container stk--no-background stk--no-padding\"><div class=\"stk-block-content stk-inner-blocks stk-1fb48d8-inner-blocks\">\n<p><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong>WordPress 3.7 «&nbsp;Count Basie&nbsp;»</strong> </strong></strong></strong></strong>apporte une fonctionnalité-clé&nbsp;: le système de mise à jour automatique des versions mineures. Plus besoin de réaliser les mises à jour à la main via son FTP et surtout, il devient possible pour l’équipe de développement de WP de déployer des mises à jour de sécurité.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">La version 3.7 sera maintenue pendant près de 10 ans (!), car son support n’a été abandonné que l’année dernière en 2022&nbsp;!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Enfin, la <strong>version 3.8 «&nbsp;Parker&nbsp;»</strong> apporte une refonte de l’interface d’admin, la faisant ressembler à ce qu’elle est aujourd’hui.</p>\n</div></div></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-columns alignwide stk-block-columns stk-block stk-ada38cc\" data-block-id=\"ada38cc\">.stk-ada38cc .stk--block-align-ada38cc{align-items:center !important}.stk-ada38cc{border-radius:1px !important;overflow:hidden !important;box-shadow:0 5px 30px -10px rgba(18,63,82,0.3) !important;padding-right:20px !important;margin-bottom:50px !important}.stk-ada38cc &gt; .stk-separator__bottom svg{filter:drop-shadow(0px 0 2px rgba(120,120,120,0.5)) !important}.stk-ada38cc-column{--stk-column-gap:45px !important}<div class=\"stk-row stk-inner-blocks stk--block-align-ada38cc stk-block-content stk-content-align stk-ada38cc-column alignwide\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-column stk-block-column stk-column stk-block stk-368a14e stk-block-background stk--has-background-overlay\" data-v=\"4\" data-block-id=\"368a14e\">.stk-368a14e{align-self:center !important;background-image:url(https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/group-1871.jpg) !important;background-repeat:no-repeat !important;background-size:cover !important}.stk-368a14e-inner-blocks{justify-content:center !important}.stk-368a14e-container{min-height:250px !important}@media screen and (min-width:768px){.stk-368a14e{flex:1 1 33.3% !important}}<div class=\"stk-column-wrapper stk-block-column__content stk-container stk-368a14e-container stk--no-background stk--no-padding\"><div class=\"stk--column-flex stk-block-content stk-inner-blocks stk-368a14e-inner-blocks\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-text stk-block-text stk-block stk-ea3392e\" data-block-id=\"ea3392e\">.stk-ea3392e .stk-block-text__text{font-size:50px !important;color:var(--paletteColor5,#ffffff) !important;font-weight:900 !important}@media screen and (max-width:1023px){.stk-ea3392e .stk-block-text__text{font-size:50px !important}}<p class=\"stk-block-text__text has-text-color has-text-align-center\">2014</p></div>\n</div></div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-column stk-block-column stk-column stk-block stk-f5519cf\" data-v=\"4\" data-block-id=\"f5519cf\">.stk-f5519cf{align-self:center !important}@media screen and (min-width:768px){.stk-f5519cf{flex:1 1 66.7% !important}}<div class=\"stk-column-wrapper stk-block-column__content stk-container stk-f5519cf-container stk--no-background stk--no-padding\"><div class=\"stk-block-content stk-inner-blocks stk-f5519cf-inner-blocks\">\n<p>Naissance de l’initiative <strong><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/five-for-the-future/\"><em><span lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"lang-attribute\">Five for the Future</span></em></a></strong>, visant à encourager les entreprises vivant de WordPress à offrir 5% de leur temps à contribuer au développement du cœur du CMS, à sa traduction, et au développement de la communauté WP en général.<br>Si l&#8217;entreprise où vous travaillez utilise WordPress au quotidien, sachez que ce don de 5% de temps de travail est <strong>indispensable</strong> pour assurer le futur du CMS qui vous apporte votre business&nbsp;!</p>\n</div></div></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-columns alignwide stk-block-columns stk-block stk-166b117\" data-block-id=\"166b117\">.stk-166b117 .stk--block-align-166b117{align-items:center !important}.stk-166b117{border-radius:1px !important;overflow:hidden !important;box-shadow:0 5px 30px -10px rgba(18,63,82,0.3) !important;margin-bottom:50px !important}.stk-166b117 &gt; .stk-separator__bottom svg{filter:drop-shadow(0px 0 2px rgba(120,120,120,0.5)) !important}.stk-166b117-column{--stk-column-gap:45px !important}<div class=\"stk-row stk-inner-blocks stk--block-align-166b117 stk-block-content stk-content-align stk-166b117-column alignwide\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-stackable-column stk-block-column stk-column stk-block stk-6a31676 stk-block-background stk--has-background-overlay\" data-v=\"4\" data-block-id=\"6a31676\">.stk-6a31676{align-self:center !important;background-image:url(https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/group-1870.jpg) !important;background-repeat:no-repeat !important;background-size:cover !important}.stk-6a31676-inner-blocks{justify-content:center !important}.stk-6a31676-container{min-height:250px !important}@media screen and