r <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jendeh/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4ebdc7fc4026524108d5a9202d80243d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4ebdc7fc4026524108d5a9202d80243d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jendeh/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jendeh</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 20, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is a great plugin which helps to manage all the caching together. My site is on cloudflare pro plan and have used APO as well. But I find this plugin superior in performance!!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Made our large site super fast....</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rdholla/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8020bf5a72f3bf90c2090457035416d4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8020bf5a72f3bf90c2090457035416d4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rdholla/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rdholla</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 23, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>we have - comparatively speaking... - a large WP site.  2.5GB database, approaching 30k posts and growing fast.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Super Page Cache for Cloudflare has by far been the biggest leap forward in speed we\'ve seen on our site vs. anything we\'ve tried before.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thank you so much for this great plugin!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Wow, I wish I knew of this plugin years ago.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/markob17/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/88302debe6d0fec89732aea9da0234be?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/88302debe6d0fec89732aea9da0234be?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/markob17/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Mark <small>(markob17)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 21, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This made my sites run super fast. Very impressed. Didn\'t have to pay $5 a month to Cloudflare for APO for what appears to offer similar functionality. My sites always ran pretty fast with WP Rocket installed on the free Cloudflare plan, but this takes it up another level. My Time to First Byte is blazing fast now. That was always one thing that was less than ideal, despite being well within recommended range and considered quite fast. This cuts that in half immediately. Anyways, good stuff!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simply Great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/boabo/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a39cc58170b6ef8cf9b0158db3ce5b7f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a39cc58170b6ef8cf9b0158db3ce5b7f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/boabo/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">boabo</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 20, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I aways faced issues with cloudflare until i found this plugin. There was still a small issue with email DNS but developer solved it instantly (issue was on my side, not the plugin). Great support. Thanks a lot.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works Very Great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joaohedler/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/62bde0d71d63dae4ca964644f37bc87f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/62bde0d71d63dae4ca964644f37bc87f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joaohedler/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">joaohedler</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 9, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br />Simple, efficient and works perfectly!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">My site is faster than ever!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jorgehoffmann/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4c789f7cc77a089e538d4c5e5e5d76da?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4c789f7cc77a089e538d4c5e5e5d76da?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jorgehoffmann/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jorgehoffmann</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 7, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dispite the fact that the plugin does not handle wp_is_mobile() very well, it really delivers a blazing fast loading time with out-of-box settings. Very nice!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">it is effective</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/samtech456/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fc2a1da2db3c8ea59087c13aae153a2a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fc2a1da2db3c8ea59087c13aae153a2a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/samtech456/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">samtech456</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 4, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>plugin work great even better than litespeed and indeed increased my site speed that I host on slow server. suggestion to add features to remove some unnessary js calls although yes there are plenty of ways to do that</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:96:\"Speed up a WordPress website by caching your webpages onto global CDN using any Cloudflare Plan.\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:3:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-cloudflare-page-cache/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=2291994\";s:7:\"caption\";s:112:\"This screen shot description corresponds to screenshot-1.jpg\nStep 1 - Enter your Cloudflare\'s API Key and e-mail\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-cloudflare-page-cache/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=2291994\";s:7:\"caption\";s:87:\"This screen shot description corresponds to screenshot-2.jpg\nStep 2 - Select the domain\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-cloudflare-page-cache/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=2292001\";s:7:\"caption\";s:91:\"This screen shot description corresponds to screenshot-3.jpg\nStep 3 - Enable the page Cache\";}}s:8:\"versions\";a:32:{s:7:\"4.3.4.3\";s:75:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-cloudflare-page-cache.4.3.4.3.zip\";s:5:\"4.3.5\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-cloudflare-page-cache.4.3.5.zip\";s:5:\"4.3.6\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-cloudflare-page-cache.4.3.6.zip\";s:5:\"4.3.7\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-cloudfl